data.description: This stunning ranch home is a private oasis, nestled on 2.41 acres of serene land. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5bathrooms, and a two-car garage, this property offers plenty of space for comfortable living. Relax in front of the cozy fireplace or soak up the peaceful surroundings on the expansive enclosed porch and gazebo; both with ceilings and benches with handmade plained cedar. Gazebo features full electric and fan, creating endless opportunities for enjoyment. This home is perfect for those seeking a tranquil retreat without sacrificing convenience. Don't miss your chance to make this exquisite property your own. Your search is over. WelcomeHome!
